General Information:
The incumbent, Manav Sharma, is a researcher working in GBP Pant National Institute of Himalayan Environment for past 04 years
Research Projects:
1) Preparation of Environment Plan for Uttarkhand(ULB wise as well as a consolidated State Environment Plan)
link: https://ueppcb.uk.gov.in/pages/display/218-draft-district-environment-plan-state-environment-plan
